snippet: Environmentalists have taken to treetops in Winnsboro, Tex., to try to block bulldozers building the southern leg of the controversial Keystone XL pipeline.
abstract: Environmental activists have taken to treetops in Winnsboro, Tex, in what may be among last pitched battles to try to block bulldozers building southern leg of controversial Keystone XL pipeline.
lead_paragraph: Environmentalists have taken to treetops in Winnsboro, Tex., to try to block bulldozers building the southern leg of the controversial Keystone XL pipeline.

headline.seo: Protesters Gather at Keystone XL Site in Texas
headline.main: Last-Ditch Bid in Texas to Try to Stop Oil Pipeline
headline.print_headline: Last-Ditch Bid in Texas To Try to Stop Oil Pipeline
